{
  "text": "This study has limitations regarding the stability of the proteins after a long-term freeze period. The number of freeze-thaw cycles affects stability of the MCP-1 recombinant protein. [CITATION_1] This may be an issue for native MCP-1 stability in our samples, thus, we used samples that have not been thawed in the past.",
